extendedInfo.description: If you are Calle 13's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Calle 13's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Calle 13's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Calle 13's lyrics are here.
